-- Rona Plans to Buy Back Up to 2.5% of Shares, Acquires 5 Piercey's Stores
-- Bill Koenig
-- 2010-06-16T12:57:15Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-16/rona-says-it-plans-to-buy-back-up-to-2-5-of-its-outstanding-shares.html

          
          
             Rona Inc. said it plans to buy back
as many as 3.25 million common shares, or 2.5 percent of its
shares outstanding, between June 21 and June 20, 2011.  
          
          


  


        